# 👋 Hi, I'm Emmanuel Ezugwu (Xiggyelias)

## 🚀 Software Engineer | AI Builder | Full-Stack Developer

I build intelligent, highly automated systems that solve real-world problems. My focus is on architecture, data integrity, and creating scalable digital solutions across education, transport, communication tools, and automated media pipelines.

---

## 🧠 What I Do

* **Full-Stack Web Development:** Building robust applications using PHP, Laravel, React.js, and JavaScript.
* **AI Systems & Automation:** Engineering modular automation pipelines, smart assistants, and API-driven workflows.
* **Computer Vision:** Developing practical vision solutions like License Plate Recognition (LPR) systems.
* **Backend Architecture & API Design:** Creating high-performance, structured backends using Laravel and FastAPI.
* **System Design & Optimization:** Translating complex business logic into clean, predictable software structures.

